  <brief_title>Nutritional, Metabolic and Respiratory Status in Cystic Fibrosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter Prospective Study of Abnormalies Tolerance Glucose by the Continuous Measurement of Glucose of Nutritional Status and Breathing in the Patient With Cystic Fibrosis</official_title>
